{"tid":1721574,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要止暴制亂，回復平靜好簡單。做到以下三樣就得。","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:55:29.000Z","uid":230703,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f87a9b7c7d9de9221f0b201c07e1a160db6fe4be","tid":1721574,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"1. 林鄭 連 鄭若驊 下台 ,  先有人應該，減少做錯永不需要負責的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n2. 成立獨立調查委員會，可以查兩邊，但一定要查警暴，同濫暴。 而家問題完全係 警察+律師師告人不公而引起，只要有人負責，市民就會和平好危。<br />\n<br />\n3. 改組監警會，令警察唔可以再無法無天。<br />\n  好警察一定有，但而家問題係有D 克警無法無天，亂尼都得，所以先越尼越多人行出尼。<br />\n<br />\n我敢寫包單，如果政府/中央 肯做這三樣野，不出一星期就回復平靜，最少少左70%的人出尼。<br />\n<br />\n而香港會變返最幫到中央Cap 水的城市， Win Win 雙贏。"},{"pid":"d57d508b0aaf735c2bfc34216a2c88d39bfaefb0","tid":1721574,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"一定得"},{"pid":"391e4964e0e90a80573fdf6559f3b64cec637b8c","tid":1721574,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"借個位please <br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫手推上熱門<br />\n一個新方向 直指中共咽喉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe have a new idea to promote CCP, <br />\nDo you think it will be work? <br />\nPlease refer to following post and leave comments below. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機會嚟啦文宣組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721163</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4440e0268f328c2dd87a4f7e84aa3c1b81fa1e29","tid":1721574,"uid":953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:45:06.000Z","msg":"你都on9, 我地咁多手足比人拉左 你咁就妥協？ 當佢地condom 呀？"},{"pid":"104b4f74cd274982272af375a56f508d274cf063","tid":1721574,"uid":6626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"7474f76e729210529750a6bc48585b3315c672ac","tid":1721574,"uid":73238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"